{"tid":1280202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢一個月喊既次數係多過之前咁多年加埋","createTime":"2019-07-03T01:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T02:39:55.000Z","uid":2617,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cc488f30b538b984bd1bd15fa7624b37d907d85a","tid":1280202,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:46:29.000Z","msg":"呢一個月係咁睇新聞<br />\n好多聲音同片段都睇/聽到喊<br />\n立場條片 我未開黎睇都已經忍唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家只要聽電台有人講呢單野就已經想黎料<br />\n<br />\n我盡量都唔想係人面前喊<br />\n多數都係自己一個匿埋一邊<br />\n但係前日我一諗到林鄭點解可以冷酷無情到咁<br />\n已經唔止嬲 係覺得好悲涼<br />\n香港人點解會有一個咁無人性既首長<br />\n真係唔值得有個好d 稍為顧及社會既人<br />\n然後係地鐵就忍唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過又唔想比人覺得軟弱<br />\n喊完又要提自己<br />\n呢個係好長既戰役 唔可以咁快冧低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21793daa6b012e29cd7ec85202bb37b5711017fb","tid":1280202,"uid":2617,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:51:36.000Z","msg":"祝各位勇士平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d827d0ca9976c139f4c6d084887ae35091f14651","tid":1280202,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:53:07.000Z","msg":"樓主仲愛唔愛6撚？"},{"pid":"5bf70261844110145acb7777c622d528d7063532","tid":1280202,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d827d0ca9976c139f4c6d084887ae35091f14651","tid":1280202,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:53:07.000Z","msg":"樓主仲愛唔愛6撚？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:58:23.000Z","msg":"？？？"},{"pid":"874fa4ac6a154f1466d7b661428c7f4cc5fea72c","tid":1280202,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"